==English==

===Noun===
'''inflexibleness'''

# The quality or state of being [[inflexible]]; [[inflexibility]]; [[rigidity]]; [[firmness]].
# [[obstinacy|Obstinacy]] of will or temper; firmness of purpose that will not [[yield]] to [[importunity]] or [[persuasion]]; unbending [[pertinacity]].

